{{Quote|The Fiend of Fire, who uses the many limbs of her serpentine body to wield deadly weapons.|Description}}
'''Marilith''', also known as '''KARY''' (a mistranslation of [[Kali]]) or '''Marylis''', is the [[Four Fiends (Final Fantasy)|Fiend of Fire]] from the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. She appears in [[Mount Gulg (Final Fantasy)|Mount Gulg]] as a woman with the lower body of a snake and has six arms, each wielding a sword.

