== Etymology ==
{{Etym|Marilith}}

"Kary" was a mistranslation of the Hindu Goddess of Destruction Kali; the name change was probably an effort to avoid potential copyright issues with ''Dungeons and Dragons'' source material, similar to the changes made to the Beholder ([[Evil Eye (Final Fantasy)|Evil Eye]]).

